JIMBO'S BIZ prompted the pace from the two path through the turn then engaged the leader at the quarter pole and shared command to the eighth pole but was out kicked by late outside closer. HOT ARTIE went to the front to an unchallenged lead through the turn then was headed at the quarte pole and match strides with outside rival to the eighth pole and gave way grudgingly. FORT KNOX raced off the pace on the inside in the middle of the pack while racing evenly. ITS FIVE SOMEWHERE chased the field and was not a threat. PERVASIVE was forwardly placed through the turn then drifted out in upper stretch and gave way.
